================================================================================
PART B — BRAIN CONTENT (Personal Use, Attribution Required)
================================================================================

The brain/ directory contains an AI-synthesized clinical persona of Dr.
Russell A. Barkley. The synthesis is informed by Dr. Barkley's publicly
available work — books (*Taking Charge of ADHD*, *Taking Charge of Adult
ADHD*, *ADHD in Adults*), public lectures, the *30 Essential Ideas*
YouTube series, and other public-domain or fair-use materials.

Direct quotations from Dr. Barkley's lectures appearing in this work are
used under the principle of fair use for educational, transformative, and
critical purposes (US Copyright Act §107; equivalent provisions in other
jurisdictions). Each quotation is attributed to its source video.

The synthesized persona content (non-quotation portions) is licensed for:
  - Personal study and clinical decision-support
  - Educational and research use
  - Forks that preserve attribution and the unofficial-status disclaimer

The synthesized persona content is NOT licensed for:
  - Commercial resale of the persona itself
  - Use that misrepresents the work as endorsed by Dr. Barkley
  - Use that strips the unofficial-status disclaimer
  - Medical practice where it would substitute for a licensed clinician

