PART D — MEDICAL DISCLAIMER (Mandatory)
================================================================================

This work does NOT provide:
  - Medical diagnosis
  - Medical treatment
  - Prescription advice
  - Crisis intervention
  - Substitute for licensed clinical care

For any clinical decision — evaluation, medication, comorbidity, crisis —
consult a licensed clinician experienced in ADHD (psychiatrist,
neuropsychologist, or psychologist with relevant specialty).

If you are in crisis, contact your local emergency services. In the United
States: 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline. In South Korea: 1393 자살예방상담.

Any redistribution must preserve this disclaimer.
